e":"2020-03-13T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"大撚把退休狗做保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ce669060bfda70e716d15083d8f00c194c541b","tid":1923432,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c94d7f831d480afa5404706365b21d6ac23f3be","tid":1923432,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c66b52307f9efac0b19701a014cd24eaa88140e","tid":1923432,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qp7BOU0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQp7BOU0.png&h=14ff9e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法庭自1月29日只提供有限度服務，停擺逾月，服務自今周起逐步恢復。區域法院登記處今日重開，早上有人龍等候派籌，一度有50至60人排隊，大樓門前有顯示屏顯示籌號，需待叫號才可乘升降機上六樓登記處。300張籌已在11時前派完。有職員拒絕讓記者進入登記處採訪，又呼喝到會計部交款的律師樓職員離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者今早配戴記者證、進入大樓6樓的登記處採訪，惟途中先有保安要求記者離開，記者詢問為何不准進內，保安只稱有職員指不准記者進入。<br />\n<br />\n記者隨後要求當面跟職員了解，一名李姓職員(政治取向清晰）以不禮貌語氣要求記者離開，當問到原因時，李稱：「你問返PPRB。」記者追問：「PPRB係警察公共關係科喎？」該李姓職員再指：「我話知你問邊個，IO(新聞主任)又好乜都好，無籌就走！」並迫令記者離開。<br />\n<br />\n職員：我話唔得就唔得！<br />\n<br />\n今天進入區域法院的市民必須量體溫及戴上口罩。登記處重開後運作並不順暢，有律師樓職員為家事法庭案件到會計部繳交翻譯款項，「噚日我都有嚟會計部交錢，上晝下晝都有交，今日點解唔得？」該名律師樓職員與職員一度大聲爭論，亦被保安請走。<br />\n<br />\n他事後向本報表達不滿，「唔得都唔使咁惡，咁冇禮貌！仲要話『我話唔得就唔得！』有冇搞錯？」約十分鐘後，律師樓職員在家事法庭職員帶領下始獲准進入繳交款項。<br />\n<br />\n最後律師樓職員交款離開時，被保安要求交回籌號，職員揶揄：「走都要籌？咁痾尿使唔使攞籌呀？」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0bc8274571a85551c117504409e200c3c66ead4a","tid":1923432,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"wtf 幾時裝修法院呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248ef96ce99556963b908135f85528710a02ad96","tid":1923432,"uid":3634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"7930486af364b80454f9de012419fe169555b437","tid":1923432,"uid":205552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f542eea903a9fea782b398956fbaf1c022d2caa0","tid":1923432,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"推 噁撚心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756d3796d8f57bbc305c464d218561235b08082b","tid":1923432,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"de6227c54dfdf6adefd1b56e6393ed314953f274","tid":1923432,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c31795bc8d7e00d53b6caf09bb9e7c9dd69ef4","tid":1923432,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978ab8ede435a6946a2a4045039fe40e97d71f31","tid":1923432,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34584bc194a98129c157a4ec897ddee636d3939a","tid":1923432,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl